Package: tableR
Type: Package
Title: Flexible Table Formatting and Styling in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Craig", "Wendorf", email = "cwendorf@uwsp.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides functions to format and style data frames as neatly aligned tables
    for console output, Markdown documents, and APA-style reports. Supports 
    numeric formatting, column alignment, custom widths, captions, and saving 
    formatted tables to text files.
